# VESAsterizer Tracker Module
# Harmonic Journey - Showcasing Polyphony, Sustain & Velocity
TITLE Harmonic Journey
TEMPO 120

# FM Instruments with good sustain
FMINSTRUMENT Piano PIANO
FMINSTRUMENT EPiano EPIANO
FMINSTRUMENT Pad BRASS
INSTRUMENT Bass SAW 0.010 0.150 0.800 0.300

# Pattern 0: Intro - Simple sustained chord
PATTERN 8 1
CH 0: C-4 ... ... ... E-4 ... ... ...
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 1: Add harmony - Multiple notes sustaining together
PATTERN 8 1
CH 0: C-4 E-4 G-4 ... ... ... ... ===
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 2: Piano chords with sustain and release
PATTERN 16 2
CH 0: C-4 E-4 G-4 C-5 --- --- --- === E-4 G-4 B-4 E-5 --- --- --- ===
CH 1: C-2 ... ... ... C-2 ... ... ... E-2 ... ... ... E-2 ... ... ...
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 3: Electric piano with velocity variations (using different octaves to simulate)
PATTERN 16 2
CH 0: C-5 ... E-5 ... G-5 ... C-6 ... === --- --- --- --- --- --- ---
CH 1: --- E-4 ... G-4 ... C-5 ... E-5 ... === --- --- --- --- --- ---
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 4: Full harmony - 4 note chord
PATTERN 8 4
CH 0: C-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
CH 1: E-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
CH 2: G-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
CH 3: C-5 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 5: Pad with sustained notes
PATTERN 16 3
