CH 1: E-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ... F-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
CH 2: G-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ... A-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ===
ENDPATTERN

# Pattern 6: Piano melody over sustained chord
PATTERN 16 4
CH 0: C-5 D-5 E-5 F-5 G-5 A-5 G-5 F-5 E-5 D-5 C-5 ... ... ... ... ---
CH 1: C-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ... === --- --- --- --- --- --- ---
CH 2: E-4 ... ... ... ... ... ... ... === --- --- --- --- --- --- ---
